Release Notes for Version 3.12.4
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.4 is the 5th release in
the Errata Tool 3.12 development period. It closes [20 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes improvements to the
RPMDiff autowaive approval workflow, batch handling, bug syncing,
released package management, and a number of other bug fixes and enhancements.

